  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Executable logic tests for D3R\u00b7AC's MilestoneEscrow.sol, run on Hardhat's EVM (TVM is Solidity/EVM-compatible for the feature set this contract uses \u2014 no TRON-specific precompiles). This is a testing harness, not the deployment path \u2014 real TRON deployment goes through contracts/tron/tronbox-config.js.",
